invalid type: string "[ORIGINAL Article 121]\nArticle 121\nSentenced to a maximum imprisonment of 5 (five) years and a maximum fine of Rp. 500,000,000.00 (five hundred million rupiah):\na. any person who deliberately makes a fake or falsifies a Visa or Entry Certificate or Stay Permit with the intention of using it for himself or another person to enter or leave or remain in the Territory of Indon